        <updateDate>2020-07-29T15:13:18Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>EARLY Act Reauthorization of 2019</b><br /><br />This bill reauthorizes through FY2024 programs that raise public awareness about breast health,&nbsp;educate health care providers to encourage early detection of breast cancer, and&nbsp;provide support for young women diagnosed with breast cancer. <br /></p>]]></text>
      </summary>
